    "title": "39. Deepgram (US) — TTS ✓ STT ✓",
    "sourcePath": "/Users/tobias.winkler/Downloads/compass_artifact_wf-b33581ad-754a-4a5a-b05f-ef15056377e0_text_markdown.md",
    "markdown": "### 39. Deepgram (US) — TTS ✓ STT ✓\n\n**Status:** Active. **$200 free credit** (no expiry, no card required).\n\n**STT:** `nova-3` (streaming: $0.0077/min, pre-recorded: $0.0043/min). 45+ languages. `flux` model for conversational voice agents. Sub-300ms latency. WebSocket streaming.\n\n**TTS:** `aura-2` ($30/1M chars). 7 languages (expanding). ~90ms latency.\n\n**Voice Agent API:** Standard $0.08/min, BYO LLM+TTS $0.04/min.\n\nEU endpoint: `api.eu.deepgram.com`. SOC 2 Type 1 & 2. HIPAA. On-premise available.",
